{"tid":1748432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年區議會選舉票站調查","createTime":"2019-11-23T16:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:06:25.000Z","uid":173191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f70823dd41fe5523a5deb46aeb28f15ebea3d384","tid":1748432,"uid":173191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/exit_poll.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Fexit_poll.html&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=acfe7cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/exit_poll.html</a><br />\n<br />\n區議會網站可以見到邊個票站<br />\n會有機會會有票站調查<br />\n<br />\n以下機構會進行票站調查：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港研究協會</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n- 2015年11月22日 <br />\n【短片】【區選】「港研」票站調查員疑似為建制數票<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=de69242d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&h=063dc134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653</a><br />\n<br />\n- 立場新聞 香港研究協會 專題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/tag/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ceb341ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=9177efb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/tag/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n- 2019年 11月21日<br />\n選舉事務處：只有香港研究協會做區選票站調查<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-21-2019/57720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-21-2019%2F57720&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=481749b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-21-2019/57720</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講咁多 <br />\n除咗小心依啲票站調查之外<br />\n你係有權唔透露投票取向<br />\n做個聰明選民 聽日票站見</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b528e38247823392be87e920ce45ed173c548a8c","tid":1748432,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"住得近票站既人可以影低全日有幾多人入過票站，再交俾傳真社。<br />\n但唔好係禁區範圍影。"},{"pid":"768e9fe29df947fc8369cf79bb1f3f5339283b9a","tid":1748432,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b528e38247823392be87e920ce45ed173c548a8c","tid":1748432,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"住得近票站既人可以影低全日有幾多人入過票站，再交俾傳真社。<br />\n但唔好係禁區範圍影。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"唔好影到黑警，小心拔槍射你"},{"pid":"067aaabb57b584710620c8c9748c9f68ee0906e1","tid":1748432,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e55b0319a7405c5d8f857f0d00fcdcffa6b20173","tid":1748432,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15b6b9aa41af3851ad3e09bf71e87a4a639a1c96","tid":1748432,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,